ABOUT US
/$
$
Love global cuisine? We invite you to savor the nuanced flavors and innovative techniques of Oaxaca Club, an exciting new concept from the Restaurant & Hospitality Investment Group.
/$
/$
$
$
Picture of four men in business wear.
Picture of logo on outside sign
Interior shot of inside of restaurant
Picture of four men in business wear.
1/3
/$
/$
$
$
PRONOUNCED:
WAH
-HAH-KAH
/$
$
Inspired by travels throughout Mexico and the country's colorful, regionally distinct flavors, Oaxaca Club pays homage to the city of Oaxaca, located in Southwest Mexico.
Our fresh, delicious take on authentic Latin cuisine features local, seasonal ingredients and a nod to North Florida's coastal lifestyle.
Sample innovative tacos, flavorful moles, savory tamales, fresh seafood dishes and much more – or try our unforgettable weekend brunch!
​
No matter what time of day you visit us, Oaxaca Club's ambitious cocktail menu is sure to raise your glass. Try a variety of mezcal-based libations (as well as Oaxaca Club's privately labeled mezcal) plus tequila-based options, classics and flights.
/$
$

Connecting food & Culture
/$
$
Welcome to The Oaxaca Club - A Jax Beach Dining Destination
/$
$
Step into a world of vibrant flavors at The Oaxaca Club, where authentic Oaxacan cuisine meets the relaxed beach charm. Our Jacksonville Beach restaurant offers an unforgettable dining experience, perfect for a cozy lunch, a romantic dinner, or an inviting happy hour. With our artfully prepared moles, fresh herbs, and exquisite quesillo paired with an agave-centric cocktail bar, we are proud to be recognized as one of the best Mexican Restaurant in Jax Beach. Reserve your table today at our Oaxaca restaurant near you and enjoy fine dining in a welcoming, local atmosphere.
/$
$
RESERVE A TABLE
/$
$
Explore Our Menu – Discover Authentic Mexican Flavors
/$
$
Discover the rich taste of genuine Oaxacan traditions in every dish. Our menu features a diverse array of offerings—from tantalizing tacos and creative brunch options to sophisticated dinner fare and refreshing margaritas. Whether you are searching for top-rated Jax Beach restaurants, the best Mexican food restaurants in Jacksonville Beach or looking for a standout spot for brunch, dinner, special event, or happy hour near the ocean,  explore our menu and let your taste buds embark on a culinary adventure you won't forget.
